The paper is about improving relation extraction using side information from knowledge bases. This falls under the category of natural language processing (NLP), which is typically classified under cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also uses neural networks and machine learning techniques, which are commonly found in the sub-categories cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves working with structured data (knowledge bases), which could fall under cs.DB (Databases). Finally, the paper involves information retrieval techniques, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
